            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "1828 - وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "كُنَّ نِسَاءُ اَلنَّبِيِّ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "آلِهِ إِذَا كَانَ عَلَيْهِنَّ صِيَامٌ أَخَّرْنَ ذَلِكَ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " إِلَى "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "شَعْبَانَ كَرَاهِيَةَ أَنْ يَمْنَعْنَ رَسُولَ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "آلِهِ حَاجَتَهُ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "إِذَا كَانَ شَعْبَانُ صُمْنَ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "صَامَ مَعَهُنَّ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "كَانَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " يَقُولُ"
          }
        ]
      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:2:2:7:6",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/2/7/6",
      "text": [
        " « شَعْبَانُ شَهْرِي»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1828 - It is narrated that the wives of the Prophet (sw) (peace and blessings be upon him and his family), if they had missed obligatory fasts, would delay making them up until Sha‘ban, disliking to prevent the Messenger of Allah (swt) (peace and blessings be upon him and his family) from fulfilling his needs. When Sha‘ban arrived, they would fast, and he would fast with them.\nHe (sw) (peace and blessings be upon him and his family) used to say: \"Sha‘ban is my month.\""
        ]
      }
    },
